title: Ine.com.CCNP.Routing.and.Switching.642-813.SWITCH-iNKiSO
description:
This course will prepare you to plan, implement, and verify the complex LAN switching solutions based on Cisco's Campus Enterprise Architecture.

During the 15+ hours of online training, you will learn about switching technologies and integration of VLANs, WLANs, voice, and video into enterprise networks with detailed slides covering each of the technologies.

See: http://www.ine.com/self-paced/ccnp/bootcamps/ccnp-routing-switching-course.htm
